            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login untuk admin dan respondent menggunakan satu endpoint unified.\n\n**Rate Limit:** 5 attempts per 15 minutes per IP\n\n**Flow:**\n1. Kirim username (email) dan password\n2. Backend validasi credentials\n3. Jika berhasil, return token dan user data\n4. Frontend redirect berdasarkan role (ADMIN → /admin, RESPONDENT → /respondent)"
